#. (itstool) path: note/p
#: C/a11y-stickykeys.page:75
msgid ""
"You can also turn sticky keys on and off by clicking the <link xref=\"a11y-"
"icon\">accessibility icon</link> on the top bar and selecting <gui>Sticky "
