msgid "SSH"
msgstr "SSH"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/nautilus-connect.page:116
msgid ""
"If you have a <em>secure shell</em> account on a server, you can connect "
"using this method. Many web hosts provide SSH accounts to members so they "
